{"tid":1976081,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（麒麟又顯靈）葉劉差啲又仆街","createTime":"2020-04-17T03:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T19:49:58.000Z","uid":50386,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"9f3da282d4f45d95a4bfd3ec968bdf24fd4443b7","tid":1976081,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T03:52:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r423GM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr423GM4.jpg&h=82d96401&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tPRDvFq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtPRDvFq.jpg&h=2f030f55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【17/4 麟麟又出招?葉劉淑儀公民廣場外險摔倒】<br />\n<br />\n早上新民黨主席葉劉淑儀出席公民力量請願活動，下車時疑外套受車門勾扣失重心向前險摔倒，「醒獅」事件險再次出現，幸好「葉劉」力保不失，<br />\n<br />\n其助手稱沒大礙，並隨即參與請願，向政府表達疫情對市民生活構成問題，促政府設立失業援助金等等。<br />\n<br />\n________________________ <br />\n<br />\n攝: 何零解<br />\n________________________ <br />\n<br />\n訂閱 Yt 頻道: PSHKmediaofficial<br />\nIG : pshkinc<br />\nTw : OfficalPshk<br />\n<br />\n如果想支持PSHK記者<br />\n歡迎大家以PayPal / 轉數快資助形式捐款畀我哋<br />\nPaypal link : paypal .me/pshk100<br />\n轉數快：9992611<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/111587046907016/posts/263777385021314/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F111587046907016%2Fposts%2F263777385021314%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU9w8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=1a4bb9e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/111587046907016/posts/263777385021314/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"8f8967bba1923a03e89bd0f20ccf402fe7429328","tid":1976081,"uid":261796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T03:53:29.000Z","msg":"［再開］睇下譚得塞幾好人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1975528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1975528</a>"},{"pid":"49adad63fc1c49254b366579f753ee1f9533c6b4","tid":1976081,"uid":205339,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T03:54:3